The free mobile application of the Post of Serbia contains the following functionalities:

•  create requests to pick up Post Express items at your address or hand them over at the post office;
•  track status of your items;
•  price calculator;
•  find post office - find post offices near your current location;
•  ePhilately - buy philatelic products in our e-shop;
•  find Postal Address Code (PAK), an integral part of the address of each citizen and legal entity at the territory of the Republic of Serbia;
•  send questions, suggestions or comments.

The application is available in Serbian and English and requires Internet connection.

